    <item>
      <title>特朗普闭幕式美国的声音受到了柬埔寨的赞美</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/trump-closing-voice-of-america-draws-praise-from-china-cambodia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的举动关闭监督美国声音和亚洲无线电广播的机构，在中国和柬埔寨（Cambodia）长期以来一直对美国媒体批评。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/trump-closing-voice-of-america-draws-praise-from-china-cambodia</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 03:06:50 GMT</pubDate>
