    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，习近平将在“不远的未来”中访问华盛顿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/trump-says-xi-will-visit-washington-in-not-too-distant-future</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）表示，随着世界上两个最大的经济体之间的贸易紧张局势，中国领导人习近平将很快访问华盛顿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/trump-says-xi-will-visit-washington-in-not-too-distant-future</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 19:35:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉承诺将被驱逐到萨尔瓦多监狱的人释放</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/venezuela-pledges-to-free-citizens-deported-to-el-salvador-jail</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据国民议会领袖豪尔赫·罗德里格斯（JorgeRodríguez）称，委内瑞拉将做“任何事情”，以使数百名被美国驱逐出萨尔瓦多臭名昭著的监狱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/venezuela-pledges-to-free-citizens-deported-to-el-salvador-jail</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 18:44:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国称台湾附近的军事活动是对我们的回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/china-signals-new-military-drills-near-taiwan-are-response-to-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国认为台湾周围是新的“军事演习”，将它们与美国最近的举动联系起来，支持自我统治的群岛和所谓的独立力量的行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/china-signals-new-military-drills-near-taiwan-are-response-to-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 14:42:34 GMT</pubDate>
